overview: Ah, fall is here and college fraternity rushing begins. As each year a new group of eager boys are willing to do anything to get into the fraternity of their dreams. This movie is full of hot, hung, and horny boys ready to push themselves to the limits in order to get into the DAM Frat. Set in the basement of frathouse, these boys let you peek into the secret brotherhood that so many wonder about. Wanna know why they are close...looks like they all have a secret they share. Grab your beer and your cock and enjoy!
title: Bareback Frathouse Dungeon
